definition: tube/cylinder/to encase in sth cylindrical (such as hands in sleeves etc)

sentences.english: He usually wears a pair of high boots in winter.
sentences.chinese: 他通常在冬天穿長筒靴。

sentences.english: The boot peeked in to see if the shoe was okay.
sentences.chinese: 長筒靴悄悄窺視那鞋子是否還好。

sentences.english: The gutul is a high boot made from thin leather.
sentences.chinese: 蒙古靴是一種用皮革製作的長筒靴。

sentences.english: Two young waifs steals a pair of boots .
sentences.chinese: 兩個年輕的流浪者偷一雙長筒靴。

sentences.english: My floor is all marked up with their muddy boots.
sentences.chinese: 我的地板全讓他們那些沾滿污泥的長筒靴弄髒了。
